#*: The square was near the '''bus station''' in the new part of Antibes.

====Synonyms====
* [[bus depot]] (usually, for one bus operator).

====Usage notes====
Contrast {{term|train station}}, which can refer to ''any'' place — major or not — a train is supposed to stop to let passengers on and off.

